        "created_at": "2021-11-12T03:47:56.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Drinking beautifully. The nose has an amalgam of exotic things\u2026think mango, paw paw, rockmelon and guava. There are truffled honey notes too with some lavender. It is rich and textured, with fabulous fruit concentration and a touch of vanilla spice. The finish is long and tinged with smoky minerals</p>",
