        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/db5fbb/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-07-25T20:17:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Anyone try the '18 yet?  It just hit my market\u2026 must-buy in every vintage for me but haven\u2019t seen a note in WA or elsewhere yet.  Thanks.</p>",
