        "username": "Jonathan_Jetter",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/f07891/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-07-25T20:54:33.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I had the 2011 not long ago, first time with this wine, totally loved it. More than enough acid to age a good bit longer IMO.</p>\n<p>There\u2019s a bit of RS in this cuvee, no? Felt a touch sweet on the palate in a way I\u2019ve never quite experienced from white Burg before.</p>",
